@article.set_section "Overview", <<-SECTION
<p>This guidance is for staff and partners overseas. Use the guidance to help you reply to a UK company that is right for the opportunity it has submitted a proposal for.</p>
SECTION



@article.set_section "'Right for opportunity' explained", <<-SECTION
<p>A company is deemed to be 'Right for opportunity' if, from your research, you have determined that it:</p>
<ul>
  <li>is eligible</li>
  <li>meets the criteria of the buyer or tender</li>
  <li>has the logistical and financial capacity to deliver</li>
</ul>
SECTION



@article.set_section "What you need to do", <<-SECTION
<p>Tell the UK company what the next step is. This will be one of the following:</p>
<ul>
  <li>the company details will be forwarded on to the buyer</li>
  <li>the company and buyer will be introduced to each other</li>
  <li>the company will need to contact the buyer directly</li>
  <li>the company will be given more information about a tender</li>
</ul>
<p>Each step has a list of suggested sentences to help you write your response. If applicable, UK companies will be informed of UK export finance and the relevant country guide and DIT regional office within our internal system, so do not include this information.</p>
SECTION



@article.set_section "Forwarding company details on to the buyer", <<-SECTION
<p>You may need to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <p>let the company know who the buyer is - if the buyer is happy for you to do so</p>
    <p class="examples-list-label">Use sentences such as:</p>
    <ul class="examples-list">
      <li>The buyer is The Clothes Shop. It is a retailer with stores throughout the country. Its website is www.theclotheshop.com</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>explain what happens next</p>
    <p class="examples-list-label">You can copy and paste:</p>
    <ul class="examples-list">
      <li>I will forward your details on to the buyer. They will contact you directly if they are interested in working with you.</li>
      <li>I will forward your details on to the buyer. They will let me know if they are interested in working with you.</li>  
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
<p>You might also need to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>provide further details about the opportunity</li>
  <li>ask the company to provide more information such as relevant documents or marketing materials</li>
  <li>ask further questions on behalf of the buyer</li>
</ul>
<p class="examples-list-label">You can copy and paste the following sentences to finish your response:</p>
<ul class="examples-list">
  <li>The buyer may take a few weeks to respond or sometimes may not respond at all. Buyer priorities change all the time. We have no say in their decisions or how they work. </li>
  <li>You can copy me into your correspondence with the buyer. I’ll do my best to help you along the way.</li>
</ul>
SECTION



